            <h1 class="text-[32px] font-serif text-slate-800">《望庐山瀑布》</h1>
            <p class="text-[16px] text-slate-500">唐·李白</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-slate-300"></div>
